_items.title: JERSEY
_items.body:
• A stretch knit fabric made from polyester and elastane or viscose and elastane

• Stretchy and lightweight, wrinkle resistant, easy to wash

• Can be clingy on the body

• Commonly used in dresses.

_items.title: BRUISED POLY
_items.body:
• Textured fabric with a luxurious sheen and soft hand feel

• Strong, resilient, doesn't shrink

• Washes easily, quick to dry

• Man-made, does not have breathability of natural fabric

• Commonly used in tops.

• Knit fabric made of viscose, nylon and elastane

• Stretch and durability, comfortable

• Easy to wash, wrinkle resistant

• Warm, so not always suitable for warmer climates

• Commonly used in pants.
_items.title: PONTE

_items.body:
• Woven fabric with a smooth surface and subtle sheen

• Constructed from cotton and elastane to create stretch and keep its shape

• Works best in fitted silhouettes

• Limited uses as does not have a soft drape

• Commonly used in fitted pants.
_items.title: COTTON SATEEN
COTTON/NYLON/ELASTANE
_items.body:
• Basque shirt quality is woven from cotton, nylon, elastane

• Soft hand feel with great stretch

• Keeps its shape even after a few washes

• Commonly used in shirts.

_items.title: VISCOSE
_items.body:
• A semi man-made fibre made from wood pulp, knitted or woven

• Used in a wide variety of styles

• Silky appearance and feel

• Breathable similar to cotton

• Creases easily

• Commonly used in dresses.

_items.title: POLYESTER
_items.body:
• Man-made fibre using naturally occurring chemicals as well as synthetics

• Very versatile, strong, light weight

• Resistant to shrinking, stretching and creasing

• Doesn't breathe as well as natural fibres

• Commonly used in tops.

_items.title: POLY/VISCOSE/ELASTANE
_items.body:
• All Basque suiting made from poly/viscose/elastane

• Comfortable to wear, good stretch and recovery, maintains appearance

• No pilling, can be hand washed

• Not a 100% natural fibre, although viscose provides breathability

• Commonly used in suiting.

• Good fabric retention, due to the nylon

• Soft hand feel and not too heavy

• Viscose allows for the fabric to be breathable

• Commonly used in knitwear.

_items.title: MUST HAVES
_items.body:
Basque Must Haves will drive up to 30% of your total Basque sales so they are key to a successful season.


So please know what your Must Haves are to ensure you are in the best position possible to achieve budget and meet your customer’s needs every day.

Each month a new fashion suit will be delivered to our best performing Basque suiting stores. The styling and fabric design will reflect global trends, ensuring the suiting range is relevant and fashion right for our Basque corporate customer.
_items.title: BASQUE SUITING
BASQUE EVENTS
_items.body:
Basque Event is a curated range of 'value added dresses' in premium fabrications and elevated styling, priced at $149.95.


Key selling times are Spring Wedding Season, Spring and Autumn Racing and the Festive season for Christmas parties and work break ups.

Each month Basque will deliver exclusive new prints in each fashion story.


You and your customer can feel secure in the knowledge that all these prints are exclusive to Basque - we own the artwork and it is copyright.


The prints are designed with the customer at front of mind, reflecting the latest global trends and colour palettes.
_items.title: EXCLUSIVE PRINTS
